{"tid":174341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"出嚟做嘢愈耐，愈覺書本嘅世界先最值得留戀","createTime":"2017-03-26T17:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T00:33:49.000Z","uid":45206,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd3493a09a13d3284d2c97af438104b4a23e71f7","tid":174341,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:12:44.000Z","msg":"書本唔會欺騙你 唔會剝削你 永遠認真而且美好<br />\n<br />\n現實係，每一次行出門口見人前都會嘆氣，每一次歸家前都鬆一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n今夜見一友人，難得開懷大笑，友人話覺得我笑得好天真。<br />\n<br />\n實在好感慨，只有睇書同見呢位朋友嘅時光先真正快樂，其他嘅日子都是煎熬。<br />\n<br />\n有無在職巴絲分享下感受"},{"pid":"9ad09bc82a13dcb66de17e94971d5aa41b5d5254","tid":174341,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"覺，書本世界好單純<br />\n利申，死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a942536cf47a5ac0506cc8459422169b48548e26","tid":174341,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:30:06.000Z","msg":"有好朋友應該知足"},{"pid":"fb37650410474d0db65771c96021790efa011e21","tid":174341,"uid":4648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8b9fd9af9af3bbc17412af3c93bfe680061cb9","tid":174341,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有好朋友應該知足</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講得啱"},{"pid":"24506e33a4df22e13e5b55ce5fad9fd042ead562","tid":174341,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺，書本世界好單純<br />\n利申，死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5cd8809320149fd5cdecb61ac10df0d4a72c02","tid":174341,"uid":